name: #14 Foxana
description:
Open data from the archive of the Temple of the Seven Wonders on the planet Frox69.

Foxana is a Soothsayer from the Lost Planet of the Mobius star system.

Predicted pirate attacks. Saved a lot of lives. She is the founder of the School of Galactic Forecasts.

She died as a result of poisoning. She didn't predict her death.
